Dialogs.Dialog: Manaka
Are you not in a good mood today？
Manaka
Hey. Do you feel sick or something？
Manaka
You've been like this all day.
Manaka
Hey... Are you tired？
Manaka
Did I make you angry or what？
Manaka
Are you going to be like this all day？ Huh？
Manaka
Hey... Why are you being so quiet？
Manaka
Am I boring you？
Manaka
Is it so difficult to talk, huh？
Manaka
It's a very quiet day today. I'm kidding.
Manaka
Hey... You know what to do, don't you？
Manaka
I kind of want to be spoiled... Sort of.
Manaka
I've been waiting... I'm kidding. Hehe！
Manaka
Having fun？ Hehe！
Manaka
I wonder if you want to hold my hand... Sort of.
Manaka
Don't you like to hold hands...？
Manaka
I really think my hand is feeling lonely right now...
Manaka
Um... Yeah, I also wanted to do this.
Manaka
Yeah. I'm happy...
Manaka
Hehe, I also wanted to do this.
Manaka
Sorry. I don't feel like it now.
Manaka
I'm so sorry. Don't do this now.
Manaka
Don't do this now. Hey...
Manaka
We must look like lovers now, right？
I guess.
Um, really...？ I see. Hehe.
Manaka
Hey... Don't you feel a little embarrassed？
Well, a little.
Me too... But I'm happy. Hehe！
Manaka
You like it like this？
Well, yeah.
Ah, you're being shy. So cute. Hehe！
Manaka
Your hand is warm.
Really？
Yes. I... like warm hands... Sort of.
Manaka
As I thought. A guy's hand is so strong.
Sorry. Does it hurt？
Not at all... I mean I... like it.
Manaka
Sweaty hand...
Ah, sorry...
No... This is cute. Sort of. Hehe.
Manaka
You know... If I do this...
Wanna hold hands？
Yes... It's so embarrassing but I'm happy.
Manaka
Your hand is big...
Really？
Yeah, so big... Hey, can you hold my hand tighter？
Manaka
I really like holding hands with you.
Really？ That's great.
Hehe. That's why I won't let go. Is it okay？
Manaka
You're only holding my hand, but I...
Hm？
I can't say it... It's too embarrassing.
Manaka
It'd be bad if any of our friends saw us like this, right？
Well... I don't know.
Don't play dumb. But I also can't resist. Sorry.
Manaka
It's like I can feel what you're thinking when we do this.
Is that so？ Can you tell what I'm thinking？
Yes. I can feel it when you think about something perverted too. Hehe. Just kidding.
Manaka
You should let go of my hand.
Why？
Because I'm afraid that you might be forcing yourself to do this...
Actually, no. Don't let go.
Manaka
Is it improper for a girl to hold a guy's hand？
Not at all...
That's a relief... I can't resist anymore.
Manaka
I'm glad you're holding my hand.
I really want to hold your hand.
Yup, I was afraid that you might not want to do that... I'm kidding.
Manaka
Hey...
What？
Why am I the only one that gets so nervous？ It's not fair.
Manaka
Sorry for asking something so selfish.
Don't worry. I also feel the same way.
Thank you. Since you said that, I'll never let you go...
Manaka
Hey, want to hold it？
What？
Geez... Then, can you hold my hand tighter？
Manaka
Before we realized, we have arrived. Hehe.
Manaka
Hey, isn't it here？
Manaka
Ah, right here.
Manaka
We've finally arrived.
Manaka
We've already arrived...
Manaka
Hey, we are almost there.
Manaka
Ah, it's here.
Manaka
Hah... We finally arrived.
Manaka
Hey, you don't like to hold my hand？
Manaka
I'm sorry about earlier... It was improper, right？
Manaka
If you're getting embarrassed, it's fine... But... Never mind.
Manaka
Ah！ Such a beautiful garden.
Hmm？ The maintenance must be difficult.
But, if you do it for the one you love, it must be enjoyable.
Ah, that's right.
Living with the one you love is the best. I wish for that as well...
Manaka
Wow... Such a beautiful house.
You're right. It's like a house from a fairy tale.
Yeah. I want to live in a house like that someday...
Hmm...？ With who？
...Hey. Look at your face. You knew my answer already. Don't tease me.
Manaka
I want to live in an apartment like that.
Ah, the one that looks like a castle？ You know... They restrict their residents to rich people only...
The interior must be very beautiful... It must be nice to live there with the one you love, right？
Um, well... I'll do my best...
Hehe. I'll be cheering for you▼
Manaka
I wonder how big a room in that apartment is.
The biggest one should be around 80 square feet. The older rooms might be smaller than that.
It would be too small for us to live in together, huh？
Yeah, I guess... Eh！？
Hehe. I was speaking to myself！
Manaka
I don't think anyone lives in that house. It looks a little scary, right？
Hey, didn't you know...？ Something dreadful happened in that house...
...Geez, are you trying to scare me？
Well...
Hehe... If something came out of that house, you'd protect me, right？
Manaka
Look！ There are birds on that twig. A pair, I think.
Yeah. They're nestling close together. They must be very intimate.
Huh？
Can we be like them？ Is it okay if I get closer to you？
Manaka
Ah... On that power cable over there...
Whoa！ So many crows. Somehow, it looks like they're staring at us.
They have cute eyes, so I don't mind them staring at us... But I don't think I want to walk pass them.
It could be dangerous. Let's take a detour.
I agree. Now, I can be with you a little longer. I'll have to say thanks to those crows.
Manaka
Look. That cat really enjoys its naptime.
It sleeps on the fence. That's quite skillful.
Yeah, if that were me, I would fall immediately.
Do you move a lot when you sleep, or are you like that kitten we just saw, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Hey. How could you ask that question to a girl？
Manaka
That dog the couple over there is taking for a walk is so cute！
Ah, a Shiba Inu, right？ Look at its eyebrows. That's cool.
Yeah. If we could take a dog for a walk like that someday, it would be nice.
Yeah... Huh？
Hehe！
Manaka
Hey, did you see？ That person is walking with a sheep.
A sheep？
Yeah. He's wearing Western-style clothes. He must be raising it.
Western-style clothes...？ Are they made from wool then？
If that's the case, I feel bad for the sheep... I thought they were nice companions...
Manaka
The cloud's shapes keep changing...
Ah, we have strong wind today.
If people's feelings changed quickly like that, it would be sad.
But, my feelings won't change, so this discussion won't apply to me...
...Hehe. Okay, I got it... Ah, look！ That cloud looks like a donut！
Manaka
Ah, a shooting star！
At this hour？ I think it might be a satellite rather than a shooting star.
Geez. You have no imagination at all... The stars won't grant your wish if you're like this.
I'm worried. I wanted to wish that you and me would be happy ever after, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I've already wished for that, so you can rest assured▼ Yeah. Hehe！
Manaka
Ah, I can smell something nice right now...
Eh？ I didn't notice. What was it？
It was something that smelled really nice... Something I've never smelled before, I think.
Wow, now I'm curious...
Right？ If we pass the same place again, we might know. Maybe on our next date.
Manaka
Ah, look！ The sky over there is so dark.
You're right. Maybe it'll rain. We should hurry.
I have a folding umbrella.
Oh, then we don't have to worry about the rain. As I could expect from ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hehe. It's nice if we can get all lovey-dovey under an umbrella.
Manaka
Ah, my eyes hurt... Can you take a look？
...C-Can you？
I'm... quite nervous.
Eh？
A-Anyway, I don't see any dust in there. You should be fine！
Manaka
Hehe, such a cute couple.
Ah, they're probably in junior high.
I guess. They're holding hands. So nice...
So nice...
Hey, I wonder what they're talking about. Hehe.
Manaka
Hehe, such a cute couple... I don't know if saying cute would be rude to them.
That grandpa and grandma, they're smiling happily. They have such good vibes.
If we can be together like that when we are their age, we must be very happy.
Yeah. Let's set it as our goal then.
Hehe. Agreed！ We'll start becoming like them little by little, right？
Manaka
Ah, that guy looked exactly like you...
Which one？
He's gone already. I think he's a business man because he wore suit... Hehe...
What？
He looked cool. I can't wait to see you become like that▼
Manaka
Wow, such a beautiful woman...
She looks stylish, too！
...You can't look at her.
...Huh？
You can't. Okay, let's go！
Manaka
I think that girl over there is in grade school. She's just so full of energy.
She runs around like that without being tired.
...I'm quite jealous of her. I wish I could be a child once more. It would be more fun.
But now we're having a good time, so it's good being like this too, right？
...Yes！
Manaka
That bicycle that just passed us... That was a wrong thing to do, right？
Yes, having two people on a bicycle is against the law.
It's dangerous, right？ But somehow, I want to try that just once... If I could sit very close to you...
...Yeah, that would be nice.
Hehe. But it's absolutely not good to go against the law. We can get that close in other kinds of vehicles then▼
Manaka
Have you ever wanted to ride on a big motorbike like the one that just passed by？
Ah, the one with the sidecar？ I don't know...
I'm afraid of sitting on the back, but I think it'd be more fun like that.
All right. If I plan to buy a motorbike in the future, I'll choose that type.
Hehe！ I'm looking forward to it.
Manaka
I wonder if it's difficult to get a driver's license.
I don't know... You wanna get one？ I thought you'd say that it's dangerous or that your parents won't allow you to.
If I become a doctor in the future, I'll need a car, right？ My family runs a hospital, after all.
I see... You really thought it out.
But, if I said that I wanted to go for a drive with you, my parents wouldn't allow it. So, keep this a secret, okay？
Manaka
Ah！ Papa's car.
That luxury one！？
I thought it was, but it wasn't. Haha, you don't have to panic.
If he sees us, he'll think that I'm taking his daughter away.
Yeah, but he'll listen to us. You'll have to confront him when the time comes, okay？
(Are you serious...？)
Manaka
Ah！ An ambulance...
What's wrong？
Hey, you need to be very careful. Don't get sick or hurt yourself, okay？ I don't know what I'd do if I didn't have you...
You too. You must be careful. If I didn't have you, I would be very sad, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Okay...
Manaka
Kyaa！
What's wrong？ What happened？
N-No... I just saw something that looked like a space alien... Didn't you see it？
I didn't... You probably mistook something for it. Maybe it was a balloon？
...That might be so. Its movement was so strange, but I guess you were right. Yeah...
Manaka
There's a lion running...
Where！？ No way！ Did a lion flee from a zoo or something！？
But I don't hear anyone screaming... Ah！ You just wanted to scare me, right？ Nice job, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Y-Yes！ I just wanted to scare you！ Big success...
(Was she serious about it...？ No way...)
Manaka
Did you see that？ A fast-walking turtle！
Turtle！？
Yeah, I think it was a giant turtle. I never imagined I would see the real thing.
Could it be a radio-controlled toy？ It's too rare...
Hehe. Its eyes were so cute▼ You should have seen it.
Manaka
Wow... Hey, they make cars that look like bugs, right？
Why？
That brown car that passed us just now looked like a bug and had 2 antennas sticking out.
I don't think that kind of car exists though...
That's what I thought. But if that wasn't a car, then what could it be...？
(Something brown with antennas and looks like a bug... Huh...？)
Manaka
Ah... My favorite sumo wrestler！
Where？
He's gone...
...I think I mistook someone as him. Sorry to leave you alone.
Don't feel so down. Next time I'll chase after him with you.
...Okay！ Thank you.
Manaka
The weather is nice.
Yeah... Ah！ This way ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
It's dangerous... What are you doing？
Thank you... I couldn't imagine how I would be if I fell down there...
(Next time we come here, I have to watch out for her.)
